snippet.title: Wolfram: a Modern Wolfenstein3D Remake
snippet.description: Wolfram is a remake of Wolfenstein3D on a modern engine, Volatile3D II, with new graphics, physics and gameplay features. This is a walkthrough of E1M1 on "Easy" skill. Please visit our official website, www.wolfram.hlfx.ru for more information!
